The '''Hendanyns''' were a [[Species/Legends|species]] known for the elaborate [[Hendanyn death mask|death masks]] they created. These masks were unique in that they established a mental link with the wearer and preserved the wearer's memories. When a Hendanyn died, the mask was removed and the memories used by future generations.

==Behind the scenes==
''Star Wars'' author [[Abel G. Peña|Abel Peña]] wrote a passage for the ''[[Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide]]'' where it was stated that [[Darth Nihilus]]' [[Mask of Darth Nihilus|mask]] may have been of Hendanyn origin.<ref name="tfn">{{JCFCite|url=posts/50677352|board=Literature|thread=Obscure Droids and Ewoks comics -- translated by Abel Peña|user=[[Abel G. Peña|Halagad_Ventor]]|date=2013-04-27|time=01:11 AM|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171105191827/http://boards.theforce.net/threads/obscure-droids-and-ewoks-comics-translated-by-abel-peña.50010980/page-3}}</ref> This paragraph was ultimately cut.

